This DVD contains an odd mixture of music videos recorded from 1984-1991. The Red Hot Chili Peppers in this consist of former and present members (Anthony Kiedis, John Frusciante, Michael "Flea" Balzary, Chad Smith, Hillel Slovak, Jack Irons, Jack Sherman, and Cliff Martinez) all from the past eras. The videos are from the albums such as "Uplift Mofo Party Plan", "Mother's Milk", and "BloodSugarSexMagik".
